Format: All retail epub except Unconventional Warrior which is retail PDF.
Readers: Epub- Adobe Digital Editions, Calibre
PDF- Abode Acrobat Reader, Adobe Digital Editions etc
Every book tested on above readers with no problems.
Conversion: convert to other formats with Calibre
Eighteen books in total, all published in 2013 (a couple have previously been published as paperbacks).
